[https://github.com/Lindydancer/faceup|Faceup] is a markup language and a regression test system for FontLockMode packages, written by [[AndersLindgren|Anders Lindgren]].

It integrates into the [[Ert]] regression test system.

*Faceup* supports checking highlight of snippets of code in inline tests up to full-scale tests where earlier highlight results have been saved to a file using the faceup markup.

== Getting the package ==

The *faceup* package is located on [https://github.com/Lindydancer/faceup Github].
